### 🔴 Critical Issues

#### 1. Broken Access Control — No Authentication on `/users` (OWASP A01)

The `/users` endpoint returns **personally identifiable information (PII)** — names and email addresses — with zero authentication or authorization. Any unauthenticated request receives the full user list.

