```

---

### 🟡 Medium Issues

#### 6. No Global Error Handler — Stack Trace Leakage (OWASP A05)

Express's default error handler will send full stack traces in responses when `NODE_ENV` is not `production`. Even in production, unhandled promise rejections can crash the process.

