// Log format: method, URL, status, response time, IP
app.use(morgan(':method :url :status :response-time ms - :remote-addr'));
```

For production, ship logs to a centralized service (Datadog, Splunk, CloudWatch) and set alerts on anomalous patterns (e.g., spike in 4xx/5xx, repeated 401s).

